com.khalsa_ji.ems

Class EmployeeBrief

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.khalsa_ji.ems.EmployeeBrief

  • public class EmployeeBrief
extends java.lang.Object
    The class EmployeeBrief defines some set of properties inspired from the Employee class. It provides a layer of abstraction over the Employee class and provides limited functionality, as compared to the Employee class.
    Since:
    1.0
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Ravikiran Singh
    See Also:
    Employee, EmployeeBriefBuilder
